doSearch

Map<Integer,Integer> doSearch(String query)
Returns a Map of Airports and Rank to put in search results. An exact match will return a single-element Map. The rank is incremented each time the query matches search criteria, if the airport Rank is high according to the db and if the airport is in close proximity.

Parameters:
query - A string to try to match.
Returns:
searchResults A Map of AirportIds and ranks.
